params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The resource name of the reseller account from which to list customers. The parent takes the format: accounts/{account_id}.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Optional. The maximum number of customers to return. The service may return fewer than this value. If unspecified, at most 10 customers will be returned. The maximum value is 50; values about 50 will be coerced to 50.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: Optional. A token identifying a page of results, if other than the first one.
